  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">There are <math alttext=\"240\"><mn>240</mn>\n</math> players in a tennis competition that includes <math alttext=\"4\"><mn>4</mn>\n</math> rounds of matches. Each player in the competition will play a match against another player in round <math alttext=\"1\"><mn>1</mn>\n</math>. At the end of each round, the player who loses the match is eliminated and the player who won the match advances to the next round to play a match against another winning player. Which equation gives the number of players, <math alttext=\"p\"><mi>p</mi>\n</math>, eliminated at the end of round <math alttext=\"r\"><mi>r</mi>\n</math>, where <math alttext=\"r less than or equals 4\"><mi>r</mi><mo>&#8804;</mo><mn>4</mn></math>?</p>",
